item.title: Read This! NOW!
item.dc:creator: @Ardvark Ardvark
item.description:
@Ardvark wrote:

Well to make a no-ip all you need to do is go to www.no-ip.com and once you have signed up for an account go to “Add Host”, After that all you need to do is make a name for it. After you have done that I believe you need the No-ip Duc setup which should be somewhere on the site. Not entirely sure because I downloaded it way back. And with a 2WIRE sometimes you need to call the internet company and have them open the ports up for you to use for your server.
